{"id": "1385157604958928927", "channel_id": "1385040039448412170", "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "content": "About team building (yes most comments here are about that but here I go), I was thinking of a channel where not just anybody could post, but more with only validated teams (screenshot of cleared levels), that can clear content with the right investment (Awakers + cov + wheels). maybe do two different with whale teams pushing the limits of the game and more manageable teams that newcomers could begin invest on knowing they are good? There is something along those lines in Flare's spreadsheet, but it covers HM, not Dtide 400, dive 72000, etc.\n\nAlso maybe a place listing all the available guides and spreadsheets to date. Once again that would need some sort of validation, giving more work to the mods so idk <:please:1356053110375714817>  but it could be fun to see how different groups tend to play the game (cf. CN and NA tend to favor very different characters )", "timestamp": "2025-06-19T07:21:48.006000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}]}
